<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,428,868]" box="[151,876,463,487]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">
Type species (by monotypy)— 
<taxonomicName authority="Dyar, 1937" authorityName="Dyar" authorityYear="1937" box="[480,871,463,487]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinicornis">
<emphasis box="[480,743,463,487]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteria pectinicornis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[750,871,464,487]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Dyar, H. S. (1937) Cossidae In: Seitz, A. (Ed.), Die exotischen Großschmetterlinge, Die amerikanischen Spinner und Schwarmer, Stuttgart: Alfred Kernen, pp. 1265 - 1285." type="book chapter" year="1937">Dyar, 1937</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="299" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,428,868]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">
<taxonomicName box="[199,343,497,521]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" genus="Schreiteriana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[199,343,497,521]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was suggested as an objective replacement name for 
<taxonomicName authority="Dyar, 1937 (Fletcher &amp; Nye 1982)" authorityName="Dyar, 1937 (Fletcher &amp; Nye" authorityYear="1982" box="[927,1432,497,521]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[927,1044,497,521]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteria</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[1053,1173,498,521]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Dyar, H. S. (1937) Cossidae In: Seitz, A. (Ed.), Die exotischen Großschmetterlinge, Die amerikanischen Spinner und Schwarmer, Stuttgart: Alfred Kernen, pp. 1265 - 1285." type="book chapter" year="1937">Dyar, 1937</bibRefCitation>
(Fletcher &amp; Nye 1982)
</taxonomicName>
. The monotypic 
<taxonomicName box="[332,449,532,556]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[332,449,532,556]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was established for 
<taxonomicName authority="Dyar, 1937" authorityName="Dyar" authorityYear="1937" box="[690,1099,532,556]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinicornis">
<emphasis box="[690,959,532,556]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteria pectinicornis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[972,1099,533,556]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Dyar, H. S. (1937) Cossidae In: Seitz, A. (Ed.), Die exotischen Großschmetterlinge, Die amerikanischen Spinner und Schwarmer, Stuttgart: Alfred Kernen, pp. 1265 - 1285." type="book chapter" year="1937">Dyar, 1937</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, but it proved to be a junior homonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Melzer, 1933" authorityName="Melzer" authorityYear="1933" box="[297,565,567,591]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[297,414,567,591]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteria</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Melzer" box="[423,565,568,591]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Melzer, J. (1933) Nota previa sobre um longicornio interessante dos Andes da Argentina. Revista de Entomologia, 3, 459 - 461." type="journal article" year="1933">Melzer, 1933</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName box="[580,703,568,591]" class="Insecta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Coleoptera</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName box="[714,871,568,591]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cerambycidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[883,986,568,591]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Lamiinae">Lamiinae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[998,1113,568,591]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Parmenini">Parmenini</taxonomicName>
). 
<emphasis box="[1132,1238,567,591]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Shreiteria</emphasis>
Dyar, the original generic name for 
<taxonomicName box="[343,482,602,625]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinicornis">
<emphasis box="[343,482,602,625]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">pectinicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, was included in the Key to the 
<taxonomicName box="[840,958,602,625]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Zeuzerinae">Zeuzerinae</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[1001,1129,602,625]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Dyar, H. S. (1937) Cossidae In: Seitz, A. (Ed.), Die exotischen Großschmetterlinge, Die amerikanischen Spinner und Schwarmer, Stuttgart: Alfred Kernen, pp. 1265 - 1285." type="book chapter" year="1937">Dyar (1937</bibRefCitation>
: 1265). 
<bibRefCitation author="Schoorl" box="[1218,1435,602,625]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Schoorl, J. W. (1990) A phylogenetic study on Cossidae (Lepidoptera: Ditrysia) based on external adult morphology. Zoologische Ferhandelingen, 263, 1 ‾ 295." type="journal article" year="1990">Schoorl (1990: 227)</bibRefCitation>
calls into question the placement of 
<taxonomicName box="[536,680,636,660]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" genus="Schreiteriana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[536,680,636,660]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the 
<taxonomicName box="[754,854,637,660]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cossidae</taxonomicName>
. As an argument, Schoorl gives the peculiarities of the thorax structure of the syntype 
<taxonomicName authority="Dyar, 1937" authorityName="Dyar" authorityYear="1937" box="[506,912,671,695]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinicornis">
<emphasis box="[506,774,671,695]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteria pectinicornis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[786,912,672,695]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Dyar, H. S. (1937) Cossidae In: Seitz, A. (Ed.), Die exotischen Großschmetterlinge, Die amerikanischen Spinner und Schwarmer, Stuttgart: Alfred Kernen, pp. 1265 - 1285." type="book chapter" year="1937">Dyar, 1937</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Citation: “The thorax of 
<taxonomicName box="[1209,1348,672,695]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinicornis">
<emphasis box="[1209,1348,672,695]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">pectinicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is very similar to that in 
<taxonomicName authority="The" authorityName="The" box="[336,536,705,729]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" genus="Cossula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="magnifica">
<emphasis box="[336,536,705,729]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Cossula magnifica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
… The mesepimeron lacks a pale band. The male retinaculum has a very long base. The uncus is broad and gradually rounded. Because of these differences, especially the type of mesepimeron, 
<taxonomicName box="[151,295,775,799]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" genus="Schreiteriana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,295,775,799]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">Schreiteriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is excluded from the 
<taxonomicName box="[525,626,776,799]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cossidae</taxonomicName>
”. 
<bibRefCitation box="[646,876,776,799]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Edwards, E. D., Gentili, P., Horak, M., Kristensen, N. P. &amp; Nielsen, E. S. (1999) The Cossoid / Sesoid Assemblage In: Kristensen, N. P. (Ed.), Lepidoptera, Moths and Butterflies. Folume 1: Evolution, Systematics, and Biogeography. Handbuch der Zoologie, Berlin, New York, pp. 188 ‾ 197." type="journal article">Edwards et al. (1999)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation box="[926,1127,776,799]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Davis, S. R., Gentili-Poole, P. &amp; Mitter, C. H. (2008) A revision of the Cossulinae of Costa Rica and cladistic analysis of the world species (Lepidoptera: Cossidae). Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society, 154, 222 ‾ 277. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.2008.00406. x" type="journal article">Davis et al. (2008)</bibRefCitation>
, clearly states problems with Schoorl’s choice of characters across his study. The study of genitalia of 
<taxonomicName authority="Dyar, 1937" authorityName="Dyar" authorityYear="1937" box="[930,1239,810,833]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Schreiteria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinicornis">
<emphasis box="[930,1094,810,833]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="299">S. pectinicornis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[1109,1231,810,833]" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" refString="Dyar, H. S. (1937) Cossidae In: Seitz, A. (Ed.), Die exotischen Großschmetterlinge, Die amerikanischen Spinner und Schwarmer, Stuttgart: Alfred Kernen, pp. 1265 - 1285." type="book chapter" year="1937">Dyar, 1937</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
indicated that this taxon belongs to the subfamily 
<taxonomicName box="[486,608,845,868]" class="Insecta" family="Cossidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Zeuzerinae">Zeuzerinae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
